{"tid":194737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國駐聯合國大使：侵侵正在考慮制裁俄羅斯","createTime":"2017-04-10T07:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T11:01:58.000Z","uid":54733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed1c896d9e1f971e4d86f1ccdcda28cc1f02500","tid":194737,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpPUMhdG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpPUMhdG.jpg&h=ef7d9b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國駐聯合國大使海利今（9）日接受《CNN》專訪時表示，美國總統川普正在考慮對俄羅斯、伊朗實施新一輪的制裁；俄羅斯、伊朗近日大力抨擊美國7日空襲敘利亞政府軍空軍基地的行為。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，美國駐聯合國大使海利（Nikki Haley）今日接受《CNN》專訪時表示，川普不滿俄羅斯、伊朗支持敘利亞政府阿塞德政權，已和官員商討，並正在考慮對俄羅斯、伊朗實施新一輪的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n海利今日指出，川普政府的情資顯示，阿塞德政權確實參與了敘利亞北部城鎮汗舍孔鎮（Khan Sheikhoun）的化學武器攻擊。汗舍孔鎮化武襲擊造成包括兒童在內上百人傷亡，戰爭現場的相關景象震驚國際，並讓川普決定下令向敘利亞政府軍的空軍基地發射59枚「戰斧」巡弋飛彈。<br />\n<br />\n川普7日發動對敘利亞政府軍的空襲後，隨即遭到俄羅斯政府大力抨擊，俄羅斯並宣布中止與美國在敘國境內避免空中衝突的備忘錄；伊朗、北韓8日也先後譴責美國，伊朗總統魯哈尼（Hassan Rouhani）嗆聲美國「你是依據哪項法律或權力，對這個獨立國家發射飛彈？」，北韓外交部則稱美國空襲敘利亞是「無法饒恕」的行為。"},{"pid":"04be71a59723c13baa6fc60b755f63c24814f025","tid":194737,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2031071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2031071&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=4c74a848\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2031071&h=131f3934\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2031071</a>"},{"pid":"c2e447ba0771e7ab730d8e097c07836facbe6c3d","tid":194737,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"In trump trump ,we trust!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced73e7f3d18de459a16443d34bb6feb2a1504a4","tid":194737,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540fad9d382ac79e29e003b8022ea87e72e06021","tid":194737,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"支持俄羅斯、美國核平中東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一邊核平伊朗、一邊核平沙特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fba7f287e48b1c7b8ffa801edfef74850520a9","tid":194737,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}